These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, french, pakistani, mexican
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, snowmobile, taxi, quad-bike
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, journalist, manager, mexicancher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the mexicancher is on the far right##1
 2. the pakistani is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the mexican is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the french is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the manager is between the person who's sport is baseball and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the manager and the person driving the quad-bike##2
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the mexicancher is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Nationality      | mexican        | french       | pakistani  | dutch |
| Transport          | quad-bike     | taxi         | snowmobile     | tram    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Job           | journalist | entrepreneur | manager   | mexicancher     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

